name: WarningSignsAndSymptomsEducation
title: Warning Signs and Symptoms Education
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent procedures used to represent patients who receive education for stroke warning signs and symptoms.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Communication. The intent of this data element is to identify patients who receive education on stroke warnings signs and symptoms. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes representing education on warning signs and symptoms.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
